README
======

General build instructions: After checkout, you have to setup your
build environment with:
libtoolize
aclocal
autoconf
automake --add-missing

If any of the tools do not exist, you have to install them in your
development environment.

To build the examples and the library run
./configure
make

You can install it in /usr/local with

make install

In case you want to install in a different location, rerun
./configure --prefix=YOUR-LOCATION
make ; make install

 
